{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SuperSpec Rallycross is a top-down racer for Rallycross fans. It's a quick and casual blast of nostalgia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Retro fueled, just like you remember</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by our favorites growing up from the 80's and 90's, SuperSpec Rallycross drives just like you'd expect if you found it in the arcade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/racegif.gif?t=1734837877\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Less serious, more fun</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SuperSpec Rallycross is easy for new drivers and satisfying for enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/jumpgif.gif?t=1734837877\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Joker lap strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A joker lap is an alternate route each driver must take once during a race. Taking the joker at the perfect time and place is part of the race strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/jokergif.gif?t=1734837877\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Split-screen party play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple controls, a familiar game loop, and a charming style make SuperSpec Rallycross the perfect party game. It supports up to four players in local split-screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/splitscreengif.gif?t=1734837877\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SuperSpec Rallycross is the passion project of a solo developer inspired by classic arcade racing games. Thank you for supporting indie development\u2014your feedback is invaluable in shaping the future of the SuperSpec series! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/extras/gridgif.gif?t=1734837877\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Grand Prix</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A four-race series where points are awarded for race position, fast laps, and joker laps taken. The points leader takes all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Single Race</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A quick race with the classic Rallycross ruleset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time Trial</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A ghost race to compete against your fastest lap times and challenge friends for online leaderboard dominance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Split-Screen Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A local multiplayer experience with both Single Race and Grand Prix modes available. (Supports online play via Steam Remote Play Together.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlockable Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20 Unique circuits inspired by the sport's most beloved real-world locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12 Rallycross cars - 6 modern marvels - 6 rally icons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Random (4 Race) Cup Generator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Full Gamepad Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamepads are fully featured and are the recommended way to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Full Steam Deck Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Verified to play great on Steam Deck.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/189118f532714496daf9e335faa493b57a348a3d.jpg"},{"name":"Faster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/5adf38059278aa015d3375807395dc5be733b631.jpg"},{"name":"SuperSpec","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/2122dd7d2b58a98c907d146ddc3e65b712ade3d7.jpg"},{"name":"Grand Prix","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/cce74e9e38ca7683479db568fad78464dfacc93b.jpg"},{"name":"Single Race","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/1c0ee27d948355cfccc5b5436fbc4d23b4827acb.jpg"},{"name":"Time Trial","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/fb01794487425029a42d4b873cc71596aeec93c0.jpg"},{"name":"Split Screen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/9b16c60379de4ef5e35a04b5b10a5f4110b1dd0e.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/a6af758a20e404c70018145e42ef2a86cc8de492.jpg"},{"name":"Oops","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/a0785de7b0bc29f5cb0b8d03eb6b57cd4c4887cd.jpg"},{"name":"Fast Lap","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1501780/e92dd0f77f61d9ebef1ffa1bad96df0e574dcecc.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734837877","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/page.bg.jpg?t=1734837877","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734837877","capsu